reviews.name: Prime Wire 8-Foot 16/3 SJTW Indoor and Outdoor Extension Cord, Black
reviews.reviewText: Great extension cord - especially for the price! I bought a Black & Decker Power Station (from Walmart) but it didn't come with an extension cord to charge it. Fortunately, because of these reveiws, I knew ahead of time, and didn't become upset. I just ordered my extension cord and the B & D Power Station at the same time! Works great!
reviews.title: Exactly What I Wanted

reviews.name: Prime Wire 8-Foot 16/3 SJTW Indoor and Outdoor Extension Cord, Black
reviews.reviewText:
Needed a "shorter" extension cord for outside Christmas decorations and this was perfect. Should last for years and was at a great price.
Delivery was sooner than expected, which is always a good thing!
Would recommend to others.
reviews.title: Nice outdoor extension cord.
